document.full_text: last-minute diplomatic wrangling has derailed a deal on a transition of power in yemen despite growing u.s. pressure on president ali abdullah saleh to agree to the gulf-brokered plan and relinquish power.
document.title: yemen crisis deal collapses despite u.s. pressure
lines_and_colors: last-minute diplomatic wrangling has derailed a deal on a transition of power in yemen despite growing u.s. pressure on president ali abdullah saleh to agree to the gulf-brokered plan and relinquish power.
